Sentencas: Oriented PrBaCo2O5+delta (PBC) thin films are prepared on yttria-stabilized ZrO2 (YSZ) substrates with orientations (001), (110) and (111) via pulsed laser deposition (PLD).
Titulo: Oriented PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) experiments at various temperatures and oxygen partial pressures reveal a good oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) performance of all the thin films.
Titulo: Oriented PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, the films' performance has considerable variance.
Titulo: Oriented PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: PBC thin film deposited on (111) oriented YSZ had the best performance, followed by (110) and (001).
Titulo: Oriented PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Experiments including high resolution X-ray diffraction (XRD), X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy (XPS), atomic force microscopy (AFM), and computation, namely molecular dynamics (MD), are used to elucidate the substrate-determined orientations, examine the morphology and composition of the thin films, and to explain the variance of the ORR performance.
Titulo: Oriented PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Our results support the anisotropy of the oxygen vacancy pathway in the a-b plane and indicate that the substrate orientations can have great influence on the thin films properties.
Titulo: Oriented PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films for solid oxide fuel cells
